channel.title: Looking for partner to help set up RSPS + WebClient
channel.description:
Alright so I've been searching for a while, trying to set up my own RSPS and WebClient. After about 3 months, I have given up. I simply decided that I am not smart enough to figure it out for myself lolz. I am looking for a partner to help me set up a 317 RSPS and WebClient. I will be willing to advertise for the server of whoever helps me or pay a certain percent of donation profits or something. I would prefer that one of the following bases be used (It doesn't really matter which one)
Acrylicx Demise PK DesignX FateScape IceyyScape Lost Valentino Marc Scape RuneClear TarzanPVp TrinityPK
Have any other questions? Reply to this, or PM me. MSN = rememberscape@live.com
First person to respond with a legitimate offer that I agree to is probably the one I will choose.
I am looking for someone WITH EXPERIENCE regarding this kind of thing. Not a n00b like me lol.
